    <p><strong>Why it wins this slot:</strong> It offers the most reliable speed-to-quality ratio in the mid-price single-serve segment.</p>
    <p><strong>Retention/static behavior:</strong> Grounds cling lightly around the chute in dry weather; quick wipe every 1-2 days keeps flow clean.</p>
    <p><CtaButton href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09HDFLF2X" external>Check price on Amazon</CtaButton></p>

    <h3>2) Breville Grind Control — Best for flavor-first buyers</h3>
    <p><strong>Verdict:</strong> Buy this if cleaner cup consistency matters more than absolute speed and you are willing to maintain a burr path.</p>
