    <p><strong>Why it wins this slot:</strong> It solves space-first buying intent without forcing a pod-only compromise.</p>
    <p><strong>Retention/static behavior:</strong> Static is moderate with dry beans; quick daily brushing keeps grounds from clumping near the exit path.</p>
    <p><CtaButton href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09NRYX5K7" external>Check price on Amazon</CtaButton></p>
